          "_name": "features022",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features22\" group=\"Features\" plugins=\"Masonry\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icons\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#28348a\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon BG\" name=\"iconbg\" value=\"#6be3ff\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n      <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n      <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n    </select>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#e0e7ff\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n          <b>Features with Masonry Effect</b>\n        </h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent\n          vitae erat. Integer aliquam, lorem vitae dapibus sollicitudin, nibh\n          nisl egestas enim, ut dapibus odio augue tempus venenatis mi semper.\n        </h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row mbr-masonry\" data-masonry=\"{&quot;percentPosition&quot;: true }\">\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v1-balance-2\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Creation</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>Ley 100 de 1993 – Sistema General de Seguridad Social en Salud (SGSSS)\n</b><br>Con esta ley aprenderás cómo se creó el sistema de salud que tenemos en Colombia. Descubrirás qué significa que sea universal, solidario y cómo se organizan los servicios según el tipo de afiliación.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.minsalud.gov.co/sites/rid/Lists/BibliotecaDigital/RIDE/DE/DIJ/ley-100-de-1993.pdf\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont imind-doctor\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Promotion</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>Ley 1751 de 2015 – Ley Estatutaria de Salud\n<br></b>Este documento te ayudará a entender por qué el derecho a la salud es considerado fundamental y qué implica que toda persona pueda exigir atención médica sin importar su capacidad de pago.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.minsalud.gov.co/Normatividad_Nuevo/Ley%201751%20de%202015.pdf\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v1-local-hospital\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Branding</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>Ministerio de Salud y Protección Social\n</b><br>Aquí encontrarás información actualizada sobre las políticas públicas en salud, campañas de prevención, estadísticas y documentos oficiales. Te servirá para estar al día con las decisiones del gobierno en materia de salud.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.minsalud.gov.co/Portada/index.html\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v1-search-money\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Design</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>ADRES – Administradora de los Recursos del SGSSS\n</b><br>Este sitio te permitirá conocer cómo se manejan y distribuyen los recursos financieros del sistema de salud. Verás cómo se garantizan los pagos a hospitales y EPS, y cómo se controla el uso del dinero público.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.adres.gov.co/\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v3-notes\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Creation</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>SciELO – Biblioteca Científica Electrónica en Línea\n</b><br>Desde esta plataforma podrás leer artículos académicos sobre salud pública, calidad del sistema, y estudios de caso sobre la realidad colombiana. Es ideal para profundizar tus análisis con fuentes confiables.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.scielo.org/\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v2-design-document\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Workflow</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>Redalyc – Red de Revistas Científicas de América Latina y el Caribe\n</b><br>Aquí encontrarás investigaciones especializadas en temas sociales y de salud. Te ayudará a comprender cómo el sistema de salud afecta a diferentes poblaciones y qué mejoras se proponen desde la academia.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.redalyc.org/\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v4-microphone-2\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Workflow</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>Spotify – Podcasts sobre salud pública y seguridad social\n</b><br>Escucha voces de expertos, historias reales y análisis sobre los retos del sistema de salud en Colombia. Es una manera práctica y cercana de reforzar tus conocimientos mientras vas en el transporte o haces otras actividades.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/4OEDcoDWIpYinKL92p5UPr\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont icon54-v2-video-app-2\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Workflow</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><b>YouTube – Canal del Ministerio de Salud\n</b><br>En este canal podrás ver entrevistas, ruedas de prensa, campañas educativas y explicaciones sobre reformas. Es una forma visual y clara de entender cómo funciona y se transforma el sistema de salud en tiempo real.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/MinSaludColPrensa \" class=\"btn item-btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Visitar enlace</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
